  "id": "RAW_ca9e6e",
  "title": "从字节、百川、Bespoke Labs 3 个大模型项目，看 RL 驱动下的 Agent 技术趋势",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MjM5ODkzMzMwMQ==&mid=2650448857&idx=2&sn=5a434839e7cb3659cba4876e5eb9bf7e&subscene=0",
